---
title: Tex-Mex Cheese-Stuffed Burgers with Tomato Salsa and Potato Wedges
description: Make it cowboy style: these burgers go beyond the ordinary with Tex-Mex flavors that bring an extra kick. The beef patties are seasoned with warm Southwestern spices and stuffed with a handful of Monterey Jack cheese that oozes when you take a bite. For toppings, you’ve got a tomato salsa and spicy crema that add plenty of swagger. With some toasty roasted potato wedges on the side for good measure, this is guaranteed to be a grand ol’ time at the burger rodeo.
